Document: OfflineMultiplayerPeer
Path: godot/classes/class_offlinemultiplayerpeer.rst
Summary: Default multiplayer peer that mimics a server with no connected peers, making the SceneTree the multiplayer authority.

This is the default MultiplayerAPI.multiplayer_peer for the Node.multiplayer. It mimics the behavior of a server with no peers connected. This means that the SceneTree will act as the multiplayer authority by default. Calls to MultiplayerAPI.is_server() will return true, and calls to MultiplayerAPI.get_unique_id() will return MultiplayerPeer.TARGET_PEER_SERVER.